front.title: Skiff
front.gametext: Deploy -1 to a Tatooine site. May add 1 driver and 5 passengers. May move as a 'react.' If lost, any characters aboard may 'jump off' (disembark).
front.lore: Repulsorlift engine. 9.2 meters long. controlled by two directional steering vanes. Jabba's fleet of skiffs is maintained by Barada.
